nodes.text: Kaeden Ta'kor was a male Human residing on Nar Shaddaa around 3643 BBY, when he was killed.

Kaeden Ta'kor appears in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic as a Champion boss on Nar Shaddaa. He is not directly involved in any quests, but can be killed for loot and as part of the achievement. This article assumes 100% game completion, which means he was killed.
